@startuml
title Flusso Counterpart API - DELETE /v1/counterparts/{id}

actor Client as C
participant "Counterpart API BS (borepurposingmgmt)" as API_BS
participant "Counterpart Service BS (borepurposingmgmt)" as Service_BS
participant "Counterpart API MS (meRepurposingReg)" as API_MS
database "Database" as DB

== Richiesta di eliminazione ==
C -> API_BS : DELETE /v1/counterparts/{id}
activate API_BS

API_BS -> Service_BS : Invoca la route interna DELETE_COUNTERPART_BY_ID per la richiesta di eliminazione (id)
activate Service_BS

note right of Service_BS
HTTP_METHOD = DELETE
CONTENT_TYPE = application/json
end note

Service_BS -> API_MS : DELETE {meRepurposingRegEndPoint}/v1/counterparts/{id}
activate API_MS

API_MS -> DB : Query di eliminazione Counterpart
DB --> API_MS : Esito eliminazione OK / errore
API_MS --> Service_BS : - 204 NO CONTENT \n- Error Response 400 / 404 / 409 / 500 
deactivate API_MS

Service_BS --> API_BS : Restituisce Response
deactivate Service_BS

API_BS --> C : - 204 NO CONTENT \n- 400 / 404 / 409 / 500 Error Response 
deactivate API_BS

@enduml
